1. "On je *zatvoru* pobegao pre nego što je došla policija." (He escaped from the prison before the police arrived.)
2. "Kazna za taj zločin je pet godina *zatvora*." (The punishment for that crime is five years in prison.)
3. "On je završio *zatvor* pre dve godine." (He finished the prison two years ago.)
4. "On je osuđen na dve godine *zatvora*." (He was sentenced to two years in prison.)
5. "Ne sme da se približi *zatvoru*." (He is not allowed to approach the prison.)